active_trend.name: silly fits
active_trend.description: Silly fits are a playful, maximalist fashion trend characterized by unexpected color combinations, clashing prints, and an abundance of whimsical accessories.  Signature pieces include oversized clothing, novelty items, and anything that defies conventional taste, resulting in a deliberately absurd and humorous aesthetic.  The overall effect is one of joyous self-expression and a rejection of seriousness.

past_trends.name: y2k
past_trends.description: Oh, darling, let's blast off to the past! Y2K fashion, short for "Year 2000," is a playful and nostalgic trend that draws inspiration from the late 90s and early 2000s. Think low-rise jeans, crop tops, platform shoes, and mini skirts, all wrapped up in a colorful and shiny package with a healthy dose of logomania and futuristic design elements – it's like a fashion party that never ended!

past_trends.name: y2k revival
past_trends.description: Oh, darling, let me take you on a blast to the past with the 'Y2K revival' trend! This early 2000s-inspired style is all about embracing bold colors, futuristic designs, and unapologetic bling. Think low-rise jeans, crop tops, platform shoes, and mini shoulder bags – it's like Paris Hilton and Britney Spears are still ruling the scene!
